rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0001
rows.name:
How could they! I want to
send them to hell, mo!

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0002
rows.name:
A report from the investigation team has
discovered a merchant ship doing business on
its own without permission from the guild, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0003
rows.name:
If they do business without following
the guild's rules, the market will
be thrown into chaos, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0004
rows.name:
If that happens, our business
will be ruined, mo!

rows.label: tlk42400013_07_msg0005
rows.name:
Could you perhaps board that
merchant ship and send them
to hell for me, mo?!
